---

---

<section
    class="med-section med-section-local"
>
    <div class="med-absolute med-inset-0 medicion-abstraction-bg med-overflow-hidden med-pointer-events-none">
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 10%">101010101010</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 30%; animation-delay: 1s">001100110011</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 50%; animation-delay: 2s">111000111000</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 70%; animation-delay: 0.5s">010101010101</div>
        <div class="data-stream" style="left: 90%; animation-delay: 1.5s">100010001000</div>
    </div>

    <div class="med-container med-text-center">
        <div class="med-mb-16">
            <span class="med-font-mono med-text-xs med-tracking-widest med-uppercase med-mb-4 med-block medicion-abstraction-tag"
                >2019</span
            >
            <h2 class="med-text-4xl med-font-bold med-mb-8 medicion-abstraction-heading">Adiós a la Materia</h2>
            <p class="med-text-lg medicion-abstraction-body">
                Jubilamos al "Gran K". Ya no confiamos en objetos que pueden ensuciarse o perder
                átomos.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="medicion-abstraction-card med-inline-block"
        >
            <p class="med-text-sm medicion-abstraction-card-title med-mb-4 med-font-bold med-uppercase med-tracking-widest">
                La Nueva Definición
            </p>
            <code class="med-text-2xl medicion-abstraction-code med-block med-mb-6 med-font-bold">
                h = 6.62607015 × 10⁻³⁴
            </code>
            <p class="med-text-sm medicion-abstraction-card-note med-mx-auto">
                Ahora el kilogramo se define fijando el valor numérico de la <strong
                    >Constante de Planck</strong
                >. Hemos atado nuestras medidas a las leyes fundamentales e inmutables del universo.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .med-section-local {
        background-color: #000000;
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .medicion-abstraction-bg {
        opacity: 0.1;
        overflow: hidden;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .medicion-abstraction-tag {
        color: #15803d;
    }

    .medicion-abstraction-heading {
        color: #4ade80;
    }

    .medicion-abstraction-body {
        color: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.8);
        line-height: 1.625;
    }

    .medicion-abstraction-card {
        background-color: #000000;
        border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .medicion-abstraction-card-title {
        color: #16a34a;
    }

    .medicion-abstraction-code {
        color: #4ade80;
    }

    .medicion-abstraction-card-note {
        color: #166534;
        max-width: 28rem;
    }

    .data-stream {
        position: absolute;
        top: -100%;
        font-size: 20px;
        writing-mode: vertical-rl;
        text-orientation: upright;
        animation: fall 5s linear infinite;
        white-space: nowrap;
        color: #0f0;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #0f0;
    }

    @keyframes fall {
        to {
            transform: translateY(200vh);
        }
    }
</style>
